                      ],
                      "text": "原神漫畫",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/21/237301566/015914bdfc4faca8a58210c8e8989e67_7757150517833651857.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "序章：風之歌",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "在巴巴托斯建立了他心愛的蒙德城後，將其交給第一批居民照顧，然後繼續前進。然而人類的貪婪是無止境的。富人控制了這座城市，並以他們認為合適的方式統治它。在這座城市著名的羽球節前夕，一位神秘的吟遊詩人來到了這座城市…",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "HoYoverse:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#37ffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "https://genshin.hoyoverse.com/zh-tw/manga/detail/104863?mute=1",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "溫迪角色預告 -「四方之風」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "我要說的故事開始於上一個千年，「南風之獅」驅除貴族，「西風之鷹」初創成型。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "「北風之狼」流浪歸來，定居狼林。四風流轉，重生的自由之城百廢待興…",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(55, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "連結：https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M9kQP-cmipY",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2021年3月10日發佈",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
